---
title: Striploin Steak and Creamy Pan Sauce with Twice-Baked Potatoes and Cheddar Broccoli
description: See you at the steakhouse? No! See you at the supper table! This special steak gets the restaurant treatment with a rich and zesty sauce.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/contre-filet-a-la-sauce-de-cuisson-cremeuse-29790fef.jpg
